已准許兩款疫苗投入試驗。其中一款的試驗對象，是中國國有企業的海外員工；另一款的對象是軍方人員。"},{"pid":"4356ce75d3d0bfe4a667965eec42ab232db90297","tid":2167533,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"公平D講，中共國又無話接種完疫苗無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1559f11d2402a3d1b64f657a2377271ae73927","tid":2167533,"uid":288913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"醒"},{"pid":"3ca94ffd408304fe29902069bf60f276ce10feaf","tid":2167533,"uid":273218,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"91308ff2e956c3cd7320c37538b779e1c8c7e2a0","tid":2167533,"uid":270073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"呢d國家一爆就慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"佢根本無爆過<br />\n所以中共真係超級賤<br />\n搵海外試藥"},{"pid":"55d2c1f2a4affc757faa38ae881d792553e40418","tid":2167533,"uid":323720,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c2d858dea493ea61235108d9ccd539a2a11e1742","tid":2167533,"uid":263581,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"最慘係連d非洲兄弟都信唔過d疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"中共自己都信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要去其他國家試"},{"pid":"57227f154f1aa0195f28cd27365e8b52d62ae3c2","tid":2167533,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"繼續天朝心態"},{"pid":"9bf9452f8e9c5b9c4bac1b2852db465636a509ec","tid":2167533,"uid":169195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"我見有樣野叫 Vaccine-induced seropositivity 唔知係咪啦<br />\n<br />\n不過總之2020年仲信中共就真係<br />\n&quot;Fool me once, shame on you. Fool me twice, shame on me. &quot;"},{"pid":"604fd8c1f3b99307